title: Readout of Jared Kushner and Jason Greenblatt’s Meeting with the Prime Minister of Israel – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
June 23, 2018
Senior Advisor Jared Kushner and Special Representative for International Negotiations Jason Greenblatt met on Saturday evening in Jerusalem, Israel with Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and Ambassador David Friedman to continue their discussions that began on Friday.
